200
00:10:35,604 --> 00:10:38,604
In summary,
benefits of anaerobic digestion

201
00:10:38,804 --> 00:10:41,377
include reduced sludge
and required footprint

202
00:10:41,577 --> 00:10:43,570
compared to aerobic treatment,

203
00:10:43,770 --> 00:10:46,770
reduces methane and sludge
for resource recovery,

204
00:10:46,970 --> 00:10:51,066
it can destroy pathogens depending
on the operating conditions.

205
00:10:52,056 --> 00:10:55,341
And drawbacks include
that the process is easily upset.

206
00:10:56,327 --> 00:11:00,341
It operates best at controlled
and consistent conditions

207
00:11:00,541 --> 00:11:03,874
and it requires knowledge 
and skill for operation.

208
